                <span className="text-[10px] font-mono text-emerald-500/60 bg-emerald-500/5 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-emerald-500/10">STABLE</span>
              </h4>
              <p className="text-slate-500 text-sm font-medium leading-relaxed">
